paragraphs.content: The Receiving Party acknowledges that some Information may be information relating to one or more identified or identifiable natural persons ("**Personal Data**") and that use of any Personal Data may be regulated by the General Data Protection Regulation (EU) 2016/679 or any other law regulating the processing of Personal Data. The Receiving Party undertakes to comply with all such applicable data privacy laws when processing such Personal Data and, if required by law, to enter into appropriate arrangements.
